About eZ Advanced Autoload
========================================================================
  This extension provides a socialnetwork bar for templating in eZPublish.
At this moment only addthis and sharethis plugins are managed.


Requirements
========================================================================
  PHP 5.3.0 or above (for namespace and lsb)
  eZPublish 4.4 or above (introduction of extension.xml elements)
 
 
Install
========================================================================
  Please read the install file place under doc folder.

  
Technical notes
========================================================================
  You can see referrals links for addthis bellow:
http://www.addthis.com/
For sharethis you can go below:
http://www.sharethis.com/